WEBVTT

00:08.080 --> 00:08.800
I remember

00:09.640 --> 00:11.240
When I was still a prince

00:11.840 --> 00:12.760
In Dong Province

00:13.080 --> 00:14.240
I had a small courtyard

00:15.040 --> 00:16.000
Smaller than the palace

00:16.240 --> 00:17.680
But in my heart

00:17.960 --> 00:19.720
It was incomparably spacious

00:20.000 --> 00:21.000
Your son remembers

00:21.680 --> 00:23.200
Often playing and fighting with elder brother

00:23.760 --> 00:25.320
Messing up Mother's flowers and plants

00:25.840 --> 00:27.040
Got many beatings from you

00:30.400 --> 00:31.560
Your mother and I

00:32.000 --> 00:33.000
Are both old now

00:33.400 --> 00:34.520
As age advances

00:34.840 --> 00:36.480
We grow sentimental

00:41.200 --> 00:42.000
In the future, your son

00:42.200 --> 00:43.000
Will often come to the palace

00:43.640 --> 00:44.760
To spend more time with Father and Mother

00:45.560 --> 00:47.160
You're a filial child

00:49.480 --> 00:50.720
Your elder brother is too

00:52.880 --> 00:53.640
Not long ago

00:54.200 --> 00:55.920
His Majesty wanted to eat Qing Province's

00:55.920 --> 00:57.280
Fresh lychees

00:57.760 --> 00:58.480
So he ordered

00:58.480 --> 01:00.320
To dig a canal

01:00.320 --> 01:01.480
Between the capital and Qing Province

01:01.720 --> 01:04.240
But corruption ran rampant

01:04.360 --> 01:06.240
Not only delaying the canal's progress

01:06.800 --> 01:08.240
But also sparking rebellion

01:08.440 --> 01:09.800
Angering His Majesty

01:09.800 --> 01:10.440
To this day

01:10.760 --> 01:11.240
Prince of Ning

01:11.240 --> 01:12.680
Remains confined in the palace

01:16.480 --> 01:17.240
Looking at the board

01:17.600 --> 01:18.400
We've reached the endgame

01:19.480 --> 01:20.600
Just one move

01:20.600 --> 01:21.480
And you can win

01:23.160 --> 01:23.840
Your turn
